## Campos y tipos clave

### `workspaces` — ltree
```php
$table->unsignedBigInteger('id')->autoIncrement();
$table->string('path')->virtualAs(null); // columna ltree nativa
// Usar DB::statement para ltree:
DB::statement('ALTER TABLE workspaces ADD COLUMN path ltree NOT NULL');
DB::statement('CREATE INDEX workspaces_path_gist ON workspaces USING GIST (path)');
```

### `invitations` — polimórfica
```php
$table->string('invitable_type');    // 'enterprise' | 'workspace'
$table->unsignedBigInteger('invitable_id');
$table->index(['invitable_type', 'invitable_id']);
```

### `activity_logs` — índices compuestos
```php
$table->index(['subject_type', 'subject_id']);
$table->index(['actor_user_id']);
$table->index(['enterprise_id', 'created_at']);
$table->index(['workspace_id', 'created_at']);
$table->index(['room_id', 'created_at']);
```

